<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Nov1931"><font color="red">27 November 1931</font> <i>Letters III and BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I am working very hard. Everything seems now to be well disposed &hellip; there has appeared in the <i>Catholic World</i> (N.Y.) an article &mdash; leader &mdash; on me which Colum and his wife say is so vulgar and scurrilous that they will not show it to me &hellip; Michael Lennon </div>
